These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, lilac, fuchsia
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, snowboarding
3 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, hedgehog
1. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the american##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
6. the japanese is the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Color           | azure        | lilac     | fuchsia    |
| Nationality   | japanese      | american     | indonesian |
| Sport         | skateboarding | snowboarding | handball   |
| Pet     | hedgehog        | goat      | lizard        |

