.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, japanese, italian
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, poppy
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the italian is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the mexican##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage    | coffee    | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Nationality       | japanese   | italian  | mexican  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| Flower   | lily | poppy    | aconite        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, tram, bus
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the bird and the oliveros-smoker##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the bike is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Transport         | bus | bike | tram |
| Cigar           | oliveros     | alhambra    | havana |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard      | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, sprite
There 3 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, august
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, goat
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating zucchini is between the owner of the goat and the person eating carrot##2
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | cola       | sprite   |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini   | kiwi     |
| Birthday         | november  | april    | august  |
| Pet   | snake | chinchilla | goat |

