.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pepper, radish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, daisy
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, nigerian, german
1. the nigerian is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking milk##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person eating pepper and the person eating radish##2
6. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
7. the nigerian is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
8. the person eating pepper is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | milk   | sprite    | cola   |
| Food          | radish | eggplant  | pepper |
| Flower   | iris   | marigold | daisy  |
| Nationality     | italian | nigerian   | german  |

