.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, canasta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, poppy
1. the person eating asparagus is the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the person who growspoppy and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Game           | bridge      | mah-jongg  | canasta |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Flower           | amaryllis      | dahlia | poppy        |

