.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, action, documentary
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, chef, electrician
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, july, december
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the chef##1
2. the accountant is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
6. the accountant is the person watching action movies##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
8. the owner of the cat is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical         | documentary      | action   |
| Job        | electrician | chef          | accountant |
| Pet        | cat         | lizard        | pony       |
| Birthday      | july       | december | october       |

