.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, thriller, horror
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, lily
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, russian, thai
1. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the russian is the russian##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the fan of classical is the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is between the argentine and the russian##2
7. the fan of d&b is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | horror     | thriller | animation  |
| Flower          | lily   | balloon-flower     | dahlia  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | blues    | classical |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai     | russian   |

