.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, reading
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, pony
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, jazz, techno
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, pall-mall, game
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | reading   | photography | fishing  |
| Pet         | pony      | lizard      | ferret   |
| Music-Genre       | jazz      | techno       | house |
| Cigar   | swisher | game       | pall-mall     |

