.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, azure
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, manager
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, sprite
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the engineer and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Color          | azure | blood-red | fuchsia |
| Job           | engineer   | manager   | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | drama     | disaster  |
| Beverage   | coffee     | sprite  | cola   |

