.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, biathlon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar, davidoff
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goat
1. the davidoff-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the bird##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Sport   | skiing | biathlon    | climbing |
| Cigar       | bolivar          | davidoff     | swisher       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Pet        | frog          | goat       | bird        |

