.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-15::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, salsa, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, canadian
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, manager, lawyer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, volleyball
1. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the australian is the manager##1
3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the designer##3
5. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
6. the lawyer is between the canadian and the australian##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre      | r&b    | salsa   | gospel      |
| Nationality   | canadian | american   | australian |
| Job           | designer      | lawyer      | manager      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | rugby      |

