1. the person who's hobby is writing is the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar      | montecristo    | tiparillo | fonseca  |
| Hobby         | singing | writing  | reading  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | epic     | thriller |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | taxi     | motorbike     |

