.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, reading, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, sprite
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, sunflower
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, rabbit
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person drinking sprite##2
6. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading      | sudoku     | collecting |
| Beverage           | coffee | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Flower   | azalea    | aconite       | sunflower      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

