.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-18::.
3 different games are played: whist, go, bridge
3 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person playing bridge is the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Game      | whist    | go        | bridge |
| Pet   | rat | ferret | fish  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile   | ship    |

