The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who growspoppy and the person watching romance movies##2
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
7. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre        | romance       | martial-arts     | epic   |
| Flower         | rose          | dahlia    | poppy       |
| Sport       | snowboarding | badminton | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | bus          | van       | skateboard |

