.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, cycling, tennis
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, pilot
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, fantasy
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, december
1. the pilot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
4. the dancer is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Sport      | tennis | cycling  | skiing |
| Job           | dancer  | pilot  | musician      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | animation     |
| Birthday           | december  | september | may         |

 